data.description: INVESTORS!!!! Within close proximity of well known University of Florida, this beautiful home includes 3 bedrooms and 1 newly renovated bath home (2022), vinyl wood floors throughout and a beautiful brick framed wood burning fire place. From the home you can walk to UF Ben Hill Griffin Stadium, Stephen C. O'Connel Center, Publix, Starbucks, the downtown Santa Fe Community College expansion, and the amazing Grove Street urban retail and entertainment neighborhood. With the zoning, you can place more beautiful dwellings in the rear of the home for an even greater positive cash flow. Don't miss out on creating a positive cash flow for immediate tenants needing a place to call home for this coming Fall 2025.
